>φ</span> : <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">j</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι₂</span>) → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">R₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">j</span>)</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">R₂</span> <span class=\"fn\">j</span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hφ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Eventually\">∀ᶠ</a> (<span class=\"fn\">j</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι₂</span>) <a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Eventually\">in</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝓕₂</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.Eventually\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Operations.html#Set.MapsTo\">Set.MapsTo</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φ</span> <span class=\"fn\">j</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">A₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">j</span>)</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">A₂</span> <span class=\"fn\">j</span>)</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/RestrictedProduct/Basic.html#RestrictedProduct\">RestrictedProduct</a> <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι₁</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">R₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι₁</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">A₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">𝓕₁</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/RestrictedProduct/Basic.html#RestrictedProduct\">RestrictedProduct</